      <title>荷兰议员奥姆茨格特因健康原因退出议员行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/dutch-lawmaker-omtzigt-to-take-a-step-back-for-health-reasons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新社会契约党领袖彼得·奥姆茨格特 (Pieter Omtzigt) 在社交媒体平台 X 上发帖称，过去的一年“异常紧张，这意味着，出于健康原因，未来几周我将更多地在幕后工作”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/dutch-lawmaker-omtzigt-to-take-a-step-back-for-health-reasons</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 13:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>竞争对手哈里斯与特朗普在庄严的世贸中心遗址纪念仪式上握手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/rivals-harris-trump-shake-hands-at-solemn-ground-zero-ceremony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯都出席了在曼哈顿世贸中心遗址举行的纪念仪式，两位为争夺白宫而激烈竞争的总统候选人齐聚这一庄严的场所，共同纪念 9·11 恐怖袭击事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/rivals-harris-trump-shake-hands-at-solemn-ground-zero-ceremony</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 13:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普媒体股价在辩论后因禁售期即将到期而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-media-shares-slide-after-debate-as-lockup-expiry-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 与总统竞选对手卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 进行辩论后，其社交媒体公司的股价周三暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-media-shares-slide-after-debate-as-lockup-expiry-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国辩论后特朗普交易进一步减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-trades-are-being-dialed-back-even-more-after-the-us-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多专家认为，唐纳德·特朗普在昨晚与竞争对手卡马拉·哈里斯的关键辩论中遭遇了明显失败，交易员们因此进一步平仓与唐纳德·特朗普入主白宫有关的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-trades-are-being-dialed-back-even-more-after-the-us-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:09:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党贵族曼德尔森未能申报其共同创立的公关公司的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/labour-peer-mandelson-fails-to-declare-large-stake-in-pr-firm-he-co-founded</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党大佬彼得·曼德尔森不得不纠正有关他拥有一家政治咨询公司股份的公开记录，此前他声称自己已将该公司全部出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/labour-peer-mandelson-fails-to-declare-large-stake-in-pr-firm-he-co-founded</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称他不愿意与哈里斯再次进行辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-says-he-s-not-inclined-toward-another-debate-with-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普最初建议在周二的论坛上增加几场对决作为补充，但他表示，自己不愿意与卡马拉·哈里斯再进行一次辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-says-he-s-not-inclined-toward-another-debate-with-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:56:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裕信银行对德国商业银行的举动令德国措手不及</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/german-government-wrong-footed-by-unicredit-move-on-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 对德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 的惊人举动令德国政府措手不及，并使德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/german-government-wrong-footed-by-unicredit-move-on-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
