      <title>两名以色列士兵在加沙直升机坠毁事件中丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-southern-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名以色列士兵昨晚在加沙地带上空因一架直升机坠毁而丧生，当时他们正执行将一名受伤士兵转移到医院的任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-southern-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 08:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非民主联盟称教育法案对联盟构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/south-africa-s-da-says-education-bill-poses-threat-to-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非第二大政党警告称，总统西里尔·拉马福萨批准修改教育立法的计划对该国联合政府构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/south-africa-s-da-says-education-bill-poses-threat-to-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 08:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯如何诱使特朗普按照她的意愿展开辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-11/harris-bet-debate-on-baiting-trump-on-abortion-project-2025-it-mostly-worked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普让自己分心，没有努力定义哈里斯，而她则强调她的核心论点，即前总统不适合担任这份工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-11/harris-bet-debate-on-baiting-trump-on-abortion-project-2025-it-mostly-worked</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 05:58:26 GMT</pubDate>
